# APNs auth keys — PASSWORD-EQUIVALENT SECRETS. Anyone with these can
# push to every app on the developer account. Never commit, never upload.
# The Mac app reads them via the Keychain (see APNsKeyStore), not from disk.
*.p8
AuthKey_*.p8
**/AuthKey_*
apns-key*
APNs-Key*

